## Technical Details

### File Structure
```
piet/
├── hello-world.png          # Our working Hello World program
├── files/
│   ├── piet                 # Working golang interpreter
│   ├── Makefile            # Build and test system
│   └── test_images/        # 15+ verified working programs
└── generation_tools/        # Python analysis and generation tools
```

### Verification Commands
```bash
# Build interpreter
cd piet/files && make clean && make

# Test our Hello World
timeout 10s ./piet ../hello-world.png 1
# Output: "Hello world!"

# Run full test suite
make test
# Result: All tests pass including original frank-zago programs
```

